Article 4(5) of Regulation (EC) No 1972/2003 is amended as follows:
1. the first indent, relating to Cyprus, is amended as follows:
(a) CN codes 0402 10, 0402 21, 0406, 1509 and 1510 are deleted;
(b) " 1517 " is replaced by " 1517 10 10, 1517 90 10, 1517 90 91, 1517 90 99 ";
(c) CN codes 2008 30 55 and 2008 30 75 are inserted;
2. the second indent, relating to the Czech Republic, is amended as follows:
(a) CN code 1517 is deleted;
(b) CN codes 0202 30 10, 0202 30 50, 2008 30 55 and 2008 30 75 are inserted;
3. the third indent, relating to Estonia, is amended as follows:
(a) " 1517 " is replaced by " 1517 10 10, 1517 10 90, 1517 90 10, 1517 90 99 ";
